3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with interference alignment in wireless networks, which is a topic that falls under networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper involves private information retrieval, which is a topic that falls under cryptography and security. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper involves the retrieval of one out of K messages from N databases, which is a topic that falls under data structures and algorithms.
